WEBVTT

00:00:55.160 --> 00:01:00.640
But also the knife,
the razor blade, the hammer

00:01:01.800 --> 00:01:04.239
and the pistol with one bullet.

00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:09.216
There are instructions which say,

00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:10.976
"I'm an object.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:14.336
You can use everything on the table on me.

00:01:14.360 --> 00:01:18.440
I'm taking all responsibility --
even killing me.

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:21.520
And the time is six hours."

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:27.400
The beginning of this
performance was easy.

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:31.856
People would give me
the glass of water to drink,